Projetc: Myhttpd
Purpose: Implementation of an http server.
Authors: Besson Dominique, Li Melissa, Mesbahi Maroua.

Usage:
	Compilation:
		./autogen.sh
		./configure
		make
	Execution:
		./myhttpd [--dry-run] server.conf
		Options:
		--dry-run: print the server's configuration and exit with value 0
		If no option is mentioned, the server would run waiting for clients and requests

Features:
	The server handles GET and CGI requests.
	Code status handling: 200, 400, 403, 404, 405, 505
